<milestone n="1" unit="juan"/>
<pb n="0536a" xml:id="T85.2779.0536a" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0536a01" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0536a02" ed="T"/><cb:docNumber>No. 2779</cb:docNumber>
<lb n="0536a03" ed="T"/><cb:juan n="001" fun="open"><cb:mulu n="1" type="卷"/><cb:jhead><note n="0536001" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">【原】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P. 2212, 【甲】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P.2204</note><note n="0536001" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: newmod-->【原】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P. 2212, 【甲】佛蘭西國民圖書館藏燉煌本, P.2204</note>佛說楞伽經禪門悉談章<note place="inline">并序</note></cb:jhead></cb:juan>
<lb n="0536a04" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0536a05" ed="T"/><cb:div type="other"><p xml:id="pT85p0536a0501">諸佛子等合掌至心聽。我今欲說大乘楞伽
<lb n="0536a06" ed="T"/>悉談章。悉談章者。悉談昔大乘在楞伽山。因
<lb n="0536a07" ed="T"/>得菩提達摩和尚。宋家元年從南<note n="0536002" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">天竹＝竺【甲】</note><note n="0536002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">天竹【大】，竺【甲】</note><app n="0536002"><lem wit="【大】">天竹</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">竺</rdg></app>國。將
<lb n="0536a08" ed="T"/>楞伽經來至東都。跋陀三藏法師奉諮翻譯。
<lb n="0536a09" ed="T"/>其經總有五卷合成一部。文字浩<note n="0536003" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">𣵡＝汗【甲】</note><note n="0536003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">𣵡【大】，汗【甲】</note><app n="0536003"><lem wit="【大】">𣵡</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">汗</rdg></app>意義難
<lb n="0536a10" ed="T"/>知。和<note n="0536004" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">上＝尚【甲】</note><note n="0536004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">上【大】，尚【甲】</note><app n="0536004"><lem wit="【大】">上</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">尚</rdg></app>慈悲廣濟<note n="0536005" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">郡品＝群生【甲】</note><note n="0536005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">郡品【大】，群生【甲】</note><app n="0536005"><lem wit="【大】">郡品</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">群生</rdg></app>。通經問道識攬<note n="0536006" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">懸＝玄【甲】</note><note n="0536006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懸【大】，玄【甲】</note><app n="0536006"><lem wit="【大】">懸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">玄</rdg></app>
<lb n="0536a11" ed="T"/>宗。窮達本原皆蒙指受。又蒿山會善沙門定
<lb n="0536a12" ed="T"/>慧翻出悉談章。廣開禪門不妨慧學。不著文
<lb n="0536a13" ed="T"/>字並合秦音。<note n="0536007" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">彼＝亦【甲】</note><note n="0536007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">彼【大】，亦【甲】</note><app n="0536007"><lem wit="【大】">彼</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">亦</rdg></app>與鳩摩羅什法師通韻。魯留
<lb n="0536a14" ed="T"/>盧樓為首。</p>
<lb n="0536a15" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536a1501"><note n="0536008" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">〔頗邏墮頗邏墮〕－【甲】</note><note n="0536008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">頗邏墮頗邏墮【大】，〔－〕【甲】</note><app n="0536008"><lem wit="【大】">頗邏墮頗邏墮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】"><space quantity="0"/></rdg></app>。第一捨緣清淨座。萬事不起
<lb n="0536a16" ed="T"/>真無我。直進菩提離因果。心心寂滅無殃禍。
<lb n="0536a17" ed="T"/>念念無念當印可。摩底利摩魯留盧樓頗羅
<lb n="0536a18" ed="T"/>墮　諸<note n="0536009" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">佛＋（弟）【甲】</note><note n="0536009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">佛【大】，佛弟【甲】</note><app n="0536009"><lem wit="【大】">佛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">佛弟</rdg></app>子莫嬾墮自勸課。愛河苦海須
<lb n="0536a19" ed="T"/><note n="0536010" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">度＝渡【甲】</note><note n="0536010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">度【大】，渡【甲】</note><app n="0536010"><lem wit="【大】">度</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">渡</rdg></app>過。憶食不喰常被餓。木頭不攢不出火。
<lb n="0536a20" ed="T"/>耶<note n="0536011" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">羅邏＝囉羅【甲】</note><note n="0536011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">羅邏【大】，囉羅【甲】</note><app n="0536011"><lem wit="【大】">羅邏</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">囉羅</rdg></app>端坐。娑訶耶莫臥。</p>
<lb n="0536a21" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536a2101"><note n="0536012" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">只＝質【甲】＊</note><note n="0536012" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><!--CBETA todo type: ＊-->只【大】＊，質【甲】＊</note><app n="0536012"><lem wit="【大】">只</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">質</rdg></app>領盛只領盛。第二住心常看淨。亦見亦聞
<lb n="0536a22" ed="T"/>無視聽。生滅兩亡由未證。從師授語方顯定。
<lb n="0536a23" ed="T"/>見佛法身無二性。性頂領徑魯留盧樓只領
<lb n="0536a24" ed="T"/>盛　諸佛子莫瞋侫。三毒忽起無佛性。癡狂
<lb n="0536a25" ed="T"/>心亂惱賢聖。眼貪色塵耳<note n="0536013" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">縛＝莫【甲】</note><note n="0536013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">縛【大】，莫【甲】</note><app n="0536013"><lem wit="【大】">縛</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">莫</rdg></app>聽。背却天堂向
<lb n="0536a26" ed="T"/>惡<note n="0536014" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">徑＝境【甲】</note><note n="0536014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">徑【大】，境【甲】</note><app n="0536014"><lem wit="【大】">徑</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">境</rdg></app>。盈令<note n="0536015" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">今＝令【甲】</note><note n="0536015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">今【大】，令【甲】</note><app n="0536015"><lem wit="【大】">今</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">令</rdg></app>修定。娑訶耶歸正。</p>
<lb n="0536a27" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536a2701"><note n="0536016" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">嗄＝復【甲】＊</note><note n="0536016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">嗄【大】＊，復【甲】＊</note><app n="0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>浪養<app type="star" corresp="#0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>浪養。第三看心須<note n="0536017" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">併＝屏【甲】</note><note n="0536017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">併【大】，屏【甲】</note><app n="0536017"><lem wit="【大】">併</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">屏</rdg></app>儻。掃却垢
<lb n="0536a28" ed="T"/>穢除災障。即色即空會無想。妄想分別是心
<lb n="0536a29" ed="T"/>量。體上識體實無謗。謗底<note n="0536018" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利謗＝裏【甲】</note><note n="0536018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利謗【大】，裏【甲】</note><app n="0536018"><lem wit="【大】">利謗</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">裏</rdg></app>魯留盧樓
<pb n="0536b" xml:id="T85.2779.0536b" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0536b01" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>浪養　諸佛子莫毀謗。一切皆有罪業障。
<lb n="0536b02" ed="T"/>他家聞聲不相放。三寸舌根作沒向。道長說
<lb n="0536b03" ed="T"/>短惱心王。心王不了說短長。來生業道受苦
<lb n="0536b04" ed="T"/>殃。羊良<note n="0536019" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">良併當＝浪屏儻【甲】</note><note n="0536019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">良併當【大】，浪屏儻【甲】</note><app n="0536019"><lem wit="【大】">良併當</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">浪屏儻</rdg></app>淨掃。堂中頃供養。</p>
<lb n="0536b05" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536b0501">拂<note n="0536020" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">粟質＝栗只【甲】＊</note><note n="0536020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">粟質【大】＊，栗只【甲】＊</note><app n="0536020"><lem wit="【大】">粟質</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">栗只</rdg></app>拂<app type="star" corresp="#0536020"><lem wit="【大】">粟質</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">栗只</rdg></app>。第四八識合六七。看心心
<lb n="0536b06" ed="T"/>本是禪室。法身身法智非一。五眼六通<note n="0536021" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">光＝廣【甲】</note><note n="0536021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">光【大】，廣【甲】</note><app n="0536021"><lem wit="【大】">光</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">廣</rdg></app>慧
<lb n="0536b07" ed="T"/>日。言下便悟實無密。密底<note n="0536022" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">利＝領【甲】＊</note><note n="0536022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">利【大】＊，領【甲】＊</note><app n="0536022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>密魯留盧樓拂
<lb n="0536b08" ed="T"/><app type="star" corresp="#0536020"><lem wit="【大】">粟質</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">栗只</rdg></app>　諸佛子莫放逸。無始已來居暗室。生
<lb n="0536b09" ed="T"/>死流轉不得出。只為愚迷障慧日。逸<note n="0536023" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">粟＝票【甲】＊</note><note n="0536023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">粟【大】＊，票【甲】＊</note><app n="0536023"><lem wit="【大】">粟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">票</rdg></app>密
<lb n="0536b10" ed="T"/>逸<app type="star" corresp="#0536023"><lem wit="【大】">粟</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">票</rdg></app>密娑訶<note n="0536024" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">直＝真【甲】</note><note n="0536024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">直【大】，真【甲】</note><app n="0536024"><lem wit="【大】">直</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">真</rdg></app>實。</p>
<lb n="0536b11" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536b1101">曉<note n="0536025" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">燎＝了【甲】＊</note><note n="0536025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">燎【大】＊，了【甲】＊</note><app n="0536025"><lem wit="【大】">燎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">了</rdg></app>曜曉<app type="star" corresp="#0536025"><lem wit="【大】">燎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">了</rdg></app>曜。第五實相門中照。一切名
<lb n="0536b12" ed="T"/>利妄呼召。如已等息貌非貌。非因非果無嗔
<lb n="0536b13" ed="T"/>㗛。性上看性妙中妙。要底裏要魯留盧樓曉
<lb n="0536b14" ed="T"/>撩曜　諸佛子莫瞋㗛。憂悲瞋㗛是障道。於
<lb n="0536b15" ed="T"/>此<note n="0536026" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">道門＝門中【甲】</note><note n="0536026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">道門【大】，門中【甲】</note><app n="0536026"><lem wit="【大】">道門</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">門中</rdg></app>無瞋㗛。澄心須看內外照。眼中有翳
<lb n="0536b16" ed="T"/>須磨曜。銅鏡不磨不中照。遙燎料作好。娑訶
<lb n="0536b17" ed="T"/>耶莫惱。</p>
<lb n="0536b18" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536b1801"><note n="0536027" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">按賴＝頞崖【甲】＊</note><note n="0536027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">按賴【大】＊，頞崖【甲】＊</note><app n="0536027"><lem wit="【大】">按賴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頞崖</rdg></app>畔按<anchor xml:id="fxT85p0536b07"/>賴畔。第六心<note n="0536028" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">離＝裏【甲】</note><note n="0536028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">離【大】，裏【甲】</note><app n="0536028"><lem wit="【大】">離</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">裏</rdg></app>禪門觀。不來不
<lb n="0536b19" ed="T"/>去無崖畔。覺上看覺除定亂。佛子與眾生同
<lb n="0536b20" ed="T"/>體段。本<note n="0536029" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">原＝元【甲】</note><note n="0536029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">原【大】，元【甲】</note><app n="0536029"><lem wit="【大】">原</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">元</rdg></app>清淨磨垢散歎。底<app type="star" corresp="#0536022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>歎魯留盧
<lb n="0536b21" ed="T"/>樓<app type="star" corresp="#0536027"><lem wit="【大】">按賴</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">頞崖</rdg></app>畔　諸佛子莫楞看。道上大有羅剎
<lb n="0536b22" ed="T"/>喚。愚人來去常繫絆。染著色塵心僚亂。行住
<lb n="0536b23" ed="T"/>坐臥無體段。在於眾中漫叫喚。得他勸諫即
<lb n="0536b24" ed="T"/>橛難。耶羅邏荼灌。娑訶耶鈍漢。</p>
<lb n="0536b25" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536b2501">普路喻普路喻。第七圓明大慧悟。四門十八
<lb n="0536b26" ed="T"/>離名數。生滅妙有懸通度。三界大師實難遇。
<lb n="0536b27" ed="T"/>生死涅槃不合渡。愛河逆上不留住。即心非
<lb n="0536b28" ed="T"/>心魔自去。去底<app type="star" corresp="#0536022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>去魯留盧樓普路喻　諸
<lb n="0536b29" ed="T"/>佛子常覺悟。一念淨心無染污。一切魔軍自
<pb n="0536c" xml:id="T85.2779.0536c" ed="T"/>
<lb n="0536c01" ed="T"/>然去。閭閭屢專注。娑訶耶大悟。</p>
<lb n="0536c02" ed="T"/><p xml:id="pT85p0536c0201"><app type="star" corresp="#0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥<app type="star" corresp="#0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥。第八禪門絕針酌。不高不
<lb n="0536c03" ed="T"/>下無樓閣。不出不入無城<note n="0536030" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">墎＝廓【甲】＊</note><note n="0536030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">墎【大】＊，廓【甲】＊</note><app n="0536030"><lem wit="【大】">墎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">廓</rdg></app>。是想<note n="0536031" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">顯＝現【甲】</note><note n="0536031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">顯【大】，現【甲】</note><app n="0536031"><lem wit="【大】">顯</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">現</rdg></app>聲即
<lb n="0536c04" ed="T"/>初學。生心動念勿令著。久坐用功作非作。無
<lb n="0536c05" ed="T"/>樂可樂是常樂。慧燈一照三千<app type="star" corresp="#0536030"><lem wit="【大】">墎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">廓</rdg></app>。定水常清
<lb n="0536c06" ed="T"/>八萬鑠。十方諸佛同開覺。覺底<app type="star" corresp="#0536022"><lem wit="【大】">利</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">領</rdg></app>博魯留
<lb n="0536c07" ed="T"/>盧樓<app type="star" corresp="#0536016"><lem wit="【大】">嗄</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">復</rdg></app>略藥　諸佛子自在作莫制約。四維
<lb n="0536c08" ed="T"/>上下不可度。住寂涅槃同門廓。甚安樂無著。
<lb n="0536c09" ed="T"/>娑訶耶等覺<note n="0536032" resp="Taisho" place="foot text" type="orig">甲本奧書曰天福陸年辛丑歲十二月十九日淨土寺□比丘僧願宗題迷頭上小自後再堪知燉煌懸公索</note>。</p></cb:div>
